title: Laser Corned Beef Products Produced Without Benefit of Import Inspection
summary: WASHINGTON, April 1, 2015 Aadji & Manten International, LLC., a Rockville, Md., establishment, is recalling approximately 1,108 pounds of canned corned beef products not presented at the U.S. point of entry for inspection, the U.S. Department of Agricultures Food Safety and Inspection Service (FSIS) announced...
